ASNA - Market Data & News
ASNA - Stock Valuation Report
 Trade 

Ascena Retail Group Inc. (ASNA) had a good day on the market for Tuesday July 25 
as 
shares jumped 9.8% to close at $2.24. About 2.33 million shares traded hands on 9,203 trades for the day, compared with an average daily volume of 
3.63 million shares out of a total float of 195.04 million. After opening the trading day at $2.05, shares of Ascena Retail Group Inc. stayed within a range of $2.34 to 
$2.05.


    With today's gains, Ascena Retail Group Inc. now has a market cap of
    $436.89 million.  Shares of Ascena Retail Group Inc. have been trading within a range of $9.12 
and $1.65 over the last year, and it had a 50-day SMA of $2.12 and a 200-day SMA of $4.37.


Ascena Retail Group Inc, through its subsidiaries, operates as a specialty retailer of apparel for women and tween girls and boys. The Company offers apparel, accessories, footwear, and lifestyle products, such as bedroom furnishings and electronics.

Ascena Retail Group Inc. is based out of Mahwah, NJ and has some 66,000 employees. Its CEO is .


